# Images

This folder contains visualizations generated during the Customer Churn Prediction project.

## Available Visualizations

- **churn_distribution.png** – Distribution of customers who churned vs. retained.
- **contract_vs_churn.png** – Churn analysis based on customer contract type.
- **monthly_charges_distribution.png** – Distribution of monthly charges.
- **tenure_distribution.png** – Customer tenure distribution.
- **correlation_heatmap.png** – Correlation matrix of numerical features.
- **feature_importance.png** – Top features influencing customer churn according to the Random Forest model.

These visualizations were created using **Matplotlib** and **Seaborn** to better understand customer behavior and evaluate model performance.
